						               													<description>An arena fighting deck builder in a world where robots have replaced human boxers. Choose one of six characters each with unqiue themes, abilities, and starting decks. When you pick your fighter select one of 5 game modes to play in ranging from solo up to a three vs three mode.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game is divided into two phases the battle and market phases. During the battle phase you play cars at the same time as your opponent. These can range from dealing damage, moving your robot, or blocking your opponent. Once each player has no more cards to play it goes to the Market Phase.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;During the market phase you gain credits used to buy from or alter the market. Use your credits to add more cards to your deck, Upgrade your robot, or clean the market.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;During gameplay you can earn titles to gain more credits or other bonuses. Don't fret if you get to zero health. Each robot can reboot and continue the fight. Be wary though each reboot has negative consequences on your robot.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Will you be the next RBL Champion?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
